title: Dungeon Mayhem: Monster Madness at the Labothéry
description:
It's time to play the best card game ever! Dungeon Mayhem is a fast-paced, Battle Royale free-for-all card game. I will provide the cards so just bring yourself and your enthusiasm! You can also make your own bubble tea at the venue!

✔️ THIS EVENT FEATURES:
 - Crafting your own Delicious bubble tea
 - Card game action satisfaction
 - Free VIP gift cards from the venue
 - Exclusive bubble tea discounts!
